        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Since s1 ≤ s2 ≤ … , k(G) + 1 is always divisible by 2s1. In particular, k(G) = 2009 forces s1 ≤ 1.",
        "bbox": [
          0.12705882352941175,
          0.4496969696969697,
